data.description: Welcome to this 4 bed/2.5 bath weston model home in Talamore! With well-maintained and newer hardwood floors on the main level and Primary bedroom, this home also features a 3 car garage. The kitchen is comprised of a beautiful island and breakfast bar, with an additional eating area in the space. Not only is the laundry closet featured on the first floor for your convenience, but you can also enjoy your work days in the office/den down the hall. Upstairs, the Primary bedroom has plenty of room, with two large walk-in closets. To top off this gorgeous spot, be sure to check out the huge basement and new brick paver patio. Talamore offers residents a clubhouse, fitness center, tennis courts, pool and trails.
